#              (0 - read in Weibull parameters, 1 - read in wind speeds)
 1
#
# NOTE: This is only present when (wflg=0)
#     wfcalm, R, (local variable) Fraction of time winds are calm (hr/hr)
#     wuc, R, (local variable) Weibull "c" factor (m/s)
